{"prompt": "Generate a website for a cybersecurity firm. The website should be bold and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>SecureNet Solutions</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #003366; /* Dark blue */\n            --secondary-color: #6699CC; /* Lighter blue */\n            --text-color: #FFFFFF;\n            --light-text: #EEEEEE;\n            --dark-background: #111111;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--dark-background);\n            color: var(--light-text);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 5px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 15px 0;\n            background-color: rgba(0, 51, 102, 0.8); /* Slightly transparent dark blue */\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); /* Subtle background element */\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0